c: 4
v: 34
t: "Raggaa u taagan (Maamulka) Haweenka, ka Fadilida Eebe Qaarkood Qaar iyo ku nafaqaynta Xoolahooda darteed, (Haweenka) Wanaagsan way Adeecaan Haaliyaanna Maqnaas- ho ilaalinta Eebe Darteed, kuwaadse ka Cabsataan Caasinimadooda waaniya, kagana Fogaada Jiifka Edbiyana, hadday idin Adeecaanna ha u dalbina Korkooda jid (inaad dhibtaan), Eebana waa Sare Wayn"